episodes.description:
@iconoclasticgypsy 
This channel's content is critical of Scientology and includes a mixture of my own streams and videos as well as content streamed by others that I find noteworthy.

It's time to hold Scientology accountable! I protest Scientology because of its past and current abuses and crimes commited against its former and current members, their families, silenced victims of s.a., vulnerable persons seeking help, the elderly, those who are critical of Scientology, and worst of all, CHILDREN who CANNOT CONSENT to the harmful activities forced onto them!  

LAPD's money-motivated loyalty to the cult of Scientology exposed a level of corruption that I wouldn't have otherwise believed had I not witnessed so many incidents where rights were violated in favor of Scientology's comfort (not the law).
